description.en:
The #1 Real-Life project involving Blockchain, not just a potential project or useless protocol, No! You will, from the 6th of September, be able to log in and get to work, collaborate, exchange and trade your resources with Yucreat.
Built with the same technology that brought Bitcoin to fame, Yucreat is a real case example of the immense possibilities Blockchain can offer. Yucreat is self governed which means it operate without human intervention following logical guidelines hardcoded into its efficiency driven algorithm.
